OL,3,CCouncil tax in Nottingham to rise to
OL,4,C4.99% as councillors approve budget
OL,6,FNottingham City councillors have voted
OL,7,Fto pass a budget which will see #17.2m
OL,8,Fof cuts to services and an almost 5%
OL,9,Fhike in council tax.
OL,11,FNottingham City Council declared
OL,12,Feffective bankruptcy in 2023 because
OL,13,Fit could not balance its books.
OL,15,FLast year's budget saw the authority
OL,16,Fraise council tax by nearly 5%, cut
OL,17,Fmore than 500 jobs and reduced public
OL,18,Fservices to plug a #53m budget gap.
