OL,3,CCouncil tax in Nottingham to rise to
OL,4,C4.99% as councillors approve budget
OL,6,FThis time around, the council's job
OL,7,Fwas made a bit easier by a #30 funding
OL,8,Finjection from the government.
OL,10,FOur political reporter, Lewis Warner,
OL,11,Fasked the Council's deputy leader,
OL,12,FEthan Radford, if it was fair for
OL,13,Fpeople in Nottingham to pay more taxes
OL,14,Fand get fewer services in return.
OL,16,FHe said: "We were in a position where
OL,17,Fwe would have to increase council tax
OL,18,Fby 10%, which no one wanted to see.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
