OL,3,CCouncil tax in Nottingham to rise to
OL,4,C4.99% as councillors approve budget
OL,6,F"We are increasing council tax by
OL,7,F4.99%, which is in line with the
OL,8,Fgovernment's tax.
OL,10,F"The bottom line would be that you
OL,11,Fcan't reverse 14 years of underfunding
OL,12,Fovernight.
OL,14,F"The point remains there are needs
OL,15,Fthat need be met. We have an enormous
OL,16,Famount of need and demand on the
OL,17,FCouncil for homelessness, social care,
OL,18,Fand children's services.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
