OL,6,F"The alternative is to not meet those
OL,7,Fneeds and I don't think anyone wants
OL,8,Fthat to happen."
OL,10,FBut one councillor wasn't convinced
OL,11,Fthe council is too strapped for cash
OL,12,Fto fund the services.
OL,14,FCouncillor Shuguftah Quddoos was a
OL,15,FLabour councillor before she was
OL,16,Fsuspended from the party for voting
OL,17,Fagainst the council's previous budget
OL,18,Fcuts.
OL,20,FShe said: "The council have a reserves
OL,21,Fpot of money for a rainy day.
