OL,6,F"In this budget, they are increasing
OL,7,Fthe reserves from #40 million to #63
OL,8,Fmillion.
OL,10,F"I'm saying let's use the reserves
OL,11,Fmoney now because it's raining and
OL,12,Fit's storming out here."
OL,14,FThese council cuts will have direct
OL,15,Fimpacts on the city's community assets.
OL,17,FLouise Holland is a trustee of the
OL,18,FSherwood Community Centre. The centre
OL,19,Fsupports many of the most vulnerable
OL,20,Fpeople in the city.
