OL,6,FThe new budget will mean the trustees
OL,7,Fwill have to take on the cost of
OL,8,Frepairing the centre.
OL,10,FShe says it worries her because
OL,11,F"repairs have been neglected for the
OL,12,Flast decade or more.
OL,14,F"Money's been whittled down and there
OL,15,Fare leaking roofs that haven't been
OL,16,Frepaired because, unless there is a
OL,17,Fthreat to life."
